<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Job Tracker</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' media='screen' href='/skill.css'>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="validation.js" defer></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Job Tracker</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="/home">Home</a>
            <a href="/">Login</a>
            <a href="applications.html">Applications</a>
            <a href="profile.html">Profile</a>
            <a href="contacts.html">Contacts</a>
            <a href="/skills">Skills</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    
        <h2>Add a skill</h2>
        <form action="/skills" method="POST">
    
    <div class="skills-form">
    <label>Type</label>
    <input type="text" name="type" placeholder="Name of Skill"/>
  
<label>Skill Level</label>
<select name="level">
    <option value="Beginner">Beginner</option>
    <option value="Intermediate">Intermediate</option>
    <option value="Advanced">Advanced</option>
</select>

<label>Category</label>
<select name="category">
    <option value="Life">Life </option>
    <option value="Technical">Technical </option>
    <option value="Leadership">Leadership </option>
    <option value="Organizational">Organizational </option>
    <option value="Other">Other</option>
</select>

    <button type="submit">Add Another</button>
</form>
<div class="description-box">
  <h3>Skill Categories Explained</h3>
  <p><strong>Life:</strong> Life skills include abilities to how you deal with daily situations and the environment. Such as personal finance or humour. </p>
  <p><strong>Technical:</strong> Technical skills include abilities to perform certain tasks. Such as programming or bookkeeping.</p>
  <p><strong>Leadership:</strong> Leadership include abilities that are usually associated with soft skills. Such as communication or decision making.</p>
  <p><strong>Organizational:</strong> Organizational include abilities that are another category of soft skills. Such as planning or analysis.</p>
  <p><strong>Other:</strong> Use this for any skill that are not part of the four categories.</p>
</div>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Name of Skill</th><th>Level</th><th>Category</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    {{#each skills}}
      <tr>
        <td>{{this.type}}</td>
        <td>{{this.level}}</td>
        <td>{{this.category}}</td>
      </tr>
    {{else}}
      <tr><td>No skills added yet.</td></tr>
    {{/each}}
  </tbody>
</table>
        </div>
    <main>
